    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a concours-level specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, complete with its signature individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential, providing an unfiltered mechanical connection. Critical preventative maintenance is fully documented, including a reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings. The chassis dynamics are factory-perfect, with original geometry and zero bushing deflection. Presented in showroom condition with a flawless undercarriage and pristine paint depth, this vehicle offers the tactile feedback and linear power delivery that defined an era of performance engineering.",
